The paper deals with deductive verification of programs that manipulate dynamic data structures using Separation Logic with inductive definitions. This suggests that the paper could belong to the Logic (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), or Formal Languages and Automata Theory (cs.FL) sub-categories. However, since the paper focuses on automated lemma generation for Separation Logic with inductive definitions, it is most likely to belong to the Logic (cs.LO) or Programming Languages (cs.PL) sub-categories. The other sub-categories are also possible, but less likely.
